1.00	Union_(comic)	Union (Dark Horse Comics)	Union is a four-issue Star Wars comic miniseries written by Michael A. Stackpole. It takes place about 20 years after the events of Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope, and chronicles the dangers and trials leading up to Luke Skywalker's wedding to Mara Jade.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/dd/Star_Wars_-_Union_01.jpg/275px-Star_Wars_-_Union_01.jpg
